title: Vertex link
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

We define the //vertex link// of a vertex $$i$$ of a 2-dimensional cell complex as the (multi)graph whose vertices are the edges that come together at $$i,$$ connected with an edge if they are part of the same face.